Rand Erases Decrease Against Dollar, Snapping Two-Day Decline

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-10-03T08:34:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/rand-erases-decrease-against-dollar-snapping-two-day-decline.html
The rand erased an earlier decline
against the dollar, rising for the first time in three days.  The South African currency strengthened 0.3 percent to
8.0767 per dollar by 10:33 a.m. in Johannesburg after earlier
retreating as much as 0.9 percent to 8.1718.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
